description:
KeePass Favicon Downloader plugin downloads and stores favicons within the KeePass database. A favicon is the little icon / logo used to identify many websites, typically displayed in the browser's address bar, bookmark list and on tabs.

* Download icons from the websites in your KeePass entries
* Make KeePass entries look more unique and easier to tell apart
* Download for an individual entry, an entire group/folder, or an arbitrary selection of entries
summary: KeePass plugin that downloads and stores favicons
author: Chris Tomlinson
